			<description><![CDATA[ <p><img src="http://cache.gawker.com/assets/images/valleywag/2008/11/billg.jpg" width="250" height="138" />Microsoft billionaire Charles Simonyi sure likes to live large. He's a <a href="http://valleywag.com/5057489/martha-stewarts-microsoft+billionaire-ex+boyfriend-to-go-back-into-space">space tourist</a>! He dates <a href="http://valleywag.com/385346/charles-simonyi-policing-hudson-river-close-enough-for-girlfriend-martha-stewart-to-wave-a-handkerchief">Martha Stewart</a>! No wait, 60-year-old Simonyi is now marrying 28-year-old Swedish socialite Lisa Persdotter! Let me guess: You don't want a photo of him. You want a photo of <em>her</em>. Here you go...</p> <p><img src="http://cache.gawker.com/assets/images/valleywag/2008/11/article_image_5f10f632249c4228.jpg" width="280" height="420" /></p> <p><em>(Photo of Bill Gates by <a href="http://www.thelocal.se/15870/20081122/">Scanpix/Adam Ihse</a>, Lisa Persdotter by <a href="http://www.stureplan.se/frame.php?main=/articles/7067/">Stureplan</a>)</em></p> ]]></description>
